title: Spookfish flying high in aerial imaging sector
text:
(MENAFN - ProactiveInvestors) Spookfish 's ( ASX:SFI ) executive chairman Jason Marinko talked to investors this week about the company's products and services in the aerial imaging sector being prepared for large scale operations in 2016.

ACCESS FULL PRESENTATION HERE 

Spookfish is targeting the government and large commercial sector users. It is also seeking alliances and licensing opportunities to accelerate global expansion.

The company continues to develop enhance and test its first generation technology demonstrator for commercial trials with major domestic and international users of geospatial data.
